Package Catalano.MachineLearning.Exploration

The Catalano.MachineLearning.Exploration namespace contains interfaces and classes for exploration algorithms of machine learning.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IExplorationPolicy
    The interface describes exploration policies, which are used in Reinforcement Learning to explore state space.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoltzmannExploration
    The class implements exploration policy base on Boltzmann distribution.
    EpsilonGreedyExploration
    The class implements epsilon greedy exploration policy.
    QLearning
    The class provides implementation of Q-Learning algorithm, known as off-policy Temporal Difference control.
    RouletteWheelExploration
    The class implements roulette whell exploration policy.
    Sarsa
    The class provides implementation of Sarse algorithm, known as on-policy Temporal Difference control.
    TabuSearchExploration
    Tabu search exploration policy.

Package Catalano.MachineLearning.Exploration Description

The Catalano.MachineLearning.Exploration namespace contains interfaces and classes for exploration algorithms of machine learning.
